data.description: Charming, move-in ready classic two-story home on a corner lot. Awesome extra large garage plus a bonus loft above perfect for a wood shop etc. This beautiful home has been very well kept with upgrades throughout! Finished large mud rooms. There’s new vinyl flooring in the kitchen and hall and newer carpet throughout. Electric has been updated, new side door, water heater, and gutters. There is a 3/4 bathroom on the main level and pantry in the kitchen. The large windows flood the dining and living room with sunshine and highlights all the gorgeous woodwork and trim! There is a spacious front double door entryway and space for a main level washer/dryer as well. The upstairs has three nice sized bedrooms with large closets and a full bathroom upstairs with a new toilet and flooring. Finally the basement is ready to create a perfect kid zone or entertainment area with a quarter bathroom. Pool table is included!
